        "title": "Why is dental core beam computer tomography useful?",
        "excerpt": "X-Ray technology has been beneficial for dentists in diagnosing dental issues. At the same time, that lacked most of the information. Dental CBCT is a much better alternative as it provides more detailed information. The process involves a cone-shaped instrument that rotates around the head of the patient to do a complete scan. Due to [&hellip;]",
        "author": "Noble Dental Care",
        "content": "<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>X-Ray technology has been beneficial for dentists in diagnosing dental issues. At the same time, that lacked most of the information. Dental CBCT is a much better alternative as it provides more detailed information. The process involves a cone-shaped instrument that rotates around the head of the patient to do a complete scan. Due to its unique working method, it brings several benefits.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote has-text-align-center\"><p>\"I think politics is like an X-ray machine: Everything is found out eventually.\"<\/p><cite>Nicolle Wallace<\/cite><\/blockquote>\n<!-- \/wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Why is dental core-beam computer tomography useful?<\/h4>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The following are the top 7 reasons why core-beam computer tomography helps diagnose dental issues.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":2334,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"https:\/\/nobledentalcares.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/31a.jpg\" alt=\"Why is dental core beam computer tomography useful?\" class=\"wp-image-2334\"\/><\/figure>\n<!-- \/wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>Dental CBCT provides 3D images with better quality<\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>One of the most significant benefits of CBCT scanning is that it allows for 3-dimensional images, which give better details with higher resolution and accuracy. Thus, it allows dentists to examine the whole affected area quickly. CBCT is effective for diagnosing and can help plan the implants to not interfere with anything else in the jaw.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>This technique can scan both soft tissues and bones<\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The traditional X-Ray technique was only effective for the bones, and no information was provided about the soft tissues. Soft tissues are often essential to be considered for diagnosing some dental issues. CBCT works on bones and soft tissues and provides more precise information for effective and pain-free treatment.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>Core-Beam Computer Tomography can tell about bone quality<\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A fantastic benefit of CBCT technology is that it can tell about bone quality. Dental procedures need good bone health, and with CBCT scans, dentists can quickly check the bone quality in a patient's mouth. Depending on different levels of bone quality, dentists can recommend other treatments for the highest success rate and least amount of pain for the patient.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>Core-Beam Computer Tomography uses less radiation<\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Traditional X-Ray technology was known for being dangerous because of a higher dose of radiation, but that is not the case with the CBCT scans. These scans use less radiation, none of which stays in the patient's body after the process. So, changes of any health issues due to those radiations prevailing inside the body also lower.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For pregnant females, it is essential to inform the dentist so that the dentist may take any crucial preventive measures.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>It is quick and painless<\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>CBCT can scan the whole mouth in less than 40 seconds and does not need to bite or clench onto something as hard as the traditional X-Ray technique. If the dentist only wants to scan a specific area, that can be done in under 10 seconds with no pain.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>While this method keeps things painless for the patients, no angles or details are missed, so the dentists are confident about getting the complete information.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>Gives a better idea about choosing the proper implantation<\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Dental implants must go inside the jaw, which may interfere with bone. With CBCT scanning, dentists can quickly check the bone structure and plan the implant accordingly. Doing so will ensure that the right implant is being used and that it is not causing any unwanted issues with the jaw bone.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>Core-Beam Computer Tomography reduces nerve damage during treatment<\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Dental implants in your mouth can often interfere with your nerves damaging them that may result in severe health issues. There could be many complications, but with CBCT scanning technology, dentists can know the exact location of the nerves and their safe working areas. In this way, the chances of nerve damage while dental treatment minimize.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Final Remarks<\/h4>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The previous techniques to diagnose dental issues were painful and time taking. However, today things are much better thanks to dental CBCT scan technology. One thing to always remember before getting it is to remove all your jewelry, hearing aid, and sunglasses so that they do not interfere with the equipment.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/nobledentalcares.com\/contacts\/\">Contact<\/a>\u00a0your dentist in Union City, Dr. Zafar Sayeedi, at<a href=\"https:\/\/nobledentalcares.com\/\">\u00a0Noble Dental Care<\/a>\u00a0to know more about why dental core beam computer tomography is useful.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>This media\/content or any other on this website does not prescribe, recommend, or prevent any treatment or procedure. Therefore, we highly recommend that you get the advice of a qualified dentist or other medical practitioners regarding your specific dental condition<\/em>.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->",
