        "title": "What are the benefits of dental crowns and bridges treatment?",
        "excerpt": "Going through bad oral health is both painful and irritating. While different individuals have different oral health situations, professionals often recommend dental crowns and dental bridges to fill the gap of an unhealthy\/missing tooth. Getting any of these treatments may benefit you in many ways. So, here we will be discussing the benefits of dental [&hellip;]",
        "author": "emily.brown@vigorant.com",
        "content": "<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Going through bad oral health is both painful and irritating. While different individuals have different oral health situations, professionals often recommend dental crowns and dental bridges to fill the gap of an unhealthy\/missing tooth. Getting any of these treatments may benefit you in many ways. So, here we will be discussing the benefits of dental crowns and dental bridges.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Benefits of dental crowns and dental bridges<\/h4>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You may enjoy the following benefits when you get dental crown and bridge treatment.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5><strong>These dental treatments may help in relieving discomfort.<\/strong><\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>One of the major use cases for dental crown treatment is to repair any structural damage. Under structural damage, the tooth becomes sensitive to both pressure and temperature. While root canal and filling treatment can repair the interior of your tooth, an external protective layer is still necessary. So, when you get these treatments, you can remove that sensitivity issue and have a comfortable feel.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5><strong>These may last for a long time.<\/strong><\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Dental crowns and dental bridges may last for a long time because of their durable material. The application process of these treatments nearly mimics the natural tooth shape and construction. Thus, these can withstand a lot of<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Grinding<\/li><li>Chewing<\/li><li>Biting<\/li><li>Trauma<\/li><\/ul>\n<!-- \/wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The results may differ depending on your usage. Besides your usage habits, regular examination and good oral hygiene are necessary. So, if you be very careful with these treatments, they can last up to 30 years without any issues. The longevity of these treatments makes them widely accepted.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5><strong>You may get a better appearing smile.<\/strong><\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"right\",\"id\":2124,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignright size-full\"><img src=\"https:\/\/nobledentalcares.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/119.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2124\"\/><\/figure>\n<!-- \/wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A missing tooth can ruin your smile, thus shattering your confidence in different stages of your life. So, if you are looking to restore that bright smile, dental crown and bridge treatment may solve the issue for you. There is a huge oral health impact, but on top of that, there is a major psychological impact as well.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thus, getting these treatments may bring a better smile to you and improve your life's quality at different stages. It is because of the confidence you will feel. However, if you want things to get even better, you must consider other dental services to get a clean and sparkling bright smile.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5><strong>Chewing and Speaking may become easier.<\/strong><\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Chewing properly is not that easy when you have a space in your mouth. It can be very painful when you have a sensitive tooth. So, the whole situation becomes very painful. Chewing different types of food can be uncomfortable and challenging. The same goes with speaking, as a missing tooth can change the overall structure of a human's oral cavity. Dental bridges and dental crowns bring a solution to all of these problems. With no additional cavity in your mouth, chewing and speaking may become easier.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5><strong>Dental crown and bridge treatment may prevent teeth from moving any further.<\/strong><\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"right\",\"id\":2125,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignright size-full\"><img src=\"https:\/\/nobledentalcares.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/118.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2125\"\/><\/figure>\n<!-- \/wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>One missing tooth can create enough space for other teeth to loosen and start falling out. Although it is not that spontaneous, this problem can be very frustrating over time.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>So, the dental bridges and dental crowns are made to fill in any space in your jaw. Thus, you can keep your teeth in their natural space by filling the gaps. Depending on your oral situation, it may lower the chances of other teeth moving any further.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5><strong>Everything is custom-made according to your jaw\u2019s shape<\/strong><\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The dental crown and bridge treatment is done separately for every individual. So, everyone can get a custom-made solution according to their jaw resulting in an overall better experience.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Final Remarks:<\/h4>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>While dental crowns and dental bridges have these potential benefits, their effectiveness may depend on your oral health situation. For some people, the experience can be better, while some may not find these treatments to be the most effective. So, for the best experience, you must consult your professional dentist to get the right treatment.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/nobledentalcares.com\/contacts\/\">Contact<\/a>\u00a0your dentist in Union City, Dr. Zafar Sayeedi at<a href=\"https:\/\/nobledentalcares.com\/\">\u00a0Noble Dental Care<\/a>\u00a0to learn more about the benefits of dental crown and bridge treatment.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>This media\/content or any other on this website does not prescribe, recommend, or prevent any treatment or procedure.\u202fTherefore, we\u202fhighly recommend that you get the advice of a qualified dentist or other medical practitioners regarding your specific dental condition<\/em>.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->",
